       trafficking, work incompatible with human dignity, failure to
       provide […] ... Read more →

Our Service

   Sherpa, a Paris-based association governed by the law of 1901, was set
   up in 2001 to protect and defend victims of economic crimes.
   Events
   Press release
   News

